{"tid":1320772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟個政權有幾黑暗先會令小朋友都害怕?","createTime":"2019-07-15T13:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T00:45:32.000Z","uid":186574,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5da984e0a00aacb226f53f33e7fa86d2644c6367","tid":1320772,"uid":186574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"以下轉自Facebook:<br />\n<br />\n//試問誰還未發聲//<br />\n<br />\n一個黑暗到點嘅地步 <br />\n先會令小朋友咁恐懼 <br />\n細心留意呢幅晝 <br />\n好令人反思同心酸...  <br />\n有啲家長會覺得小朋友未必明而唔會解釋 <br />\n有啲有心嘅家長會教導佢地嘅小朋友 <br />\n社會發生緊咩事<br />\n咁再下一代呢 再下下一代呢? <br />\n仲會唔會記得呢兩個月以來嘅歷史 <br />\n仲會唔會知道 香港人用血用汗 <br />\n甚至不惜最珍貴的生命 去爭取 <br />\n自 由 的 空 氣 <br />\n係乜野黎... <br />\n <br />\n周小朋友 <br />\n多謝你的勇敢 <br />\n希望我地一班哥哥姐姐 <br />\n甚至叔叔姨姨 <br />\n可以團結起來<br />\n爭取一啲你本來就應該擁有嘅野<br />\n<br />\n攝於荃灣連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RqMOQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RqMOQH.png&h=3c535d16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffca35eac915ff336701a88e8564e26f740bb332","tid":1320772,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"細路都知你地黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7f041300a859bcb32ababb197418fea62846bb","tid":1320772,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"小朋友有良知過黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1804f3d4f081fca0ba41365970d8ebdb7db37d4","tid":1320772,"uid":12854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:42:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警"},{"pid":"8f2960a31b73ba20593905f4fd10357cfee47452","tid":1320772,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c7f041300a859bcb32ababb197418fea62846bb","tid":1320772,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"小朋友有良知過黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,